{"about_the_game":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>There's a FIGHTSTONE right next to your heart</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Monsters lie inside all of us. They're usually asleep but they awaken once you experience turmoil. If that happens, the prospectors will come hunting for that rock in your chest</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3526190/extras/Fightstone.gif?t=1740758970\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Train your FIGHTSTONE so that a monster doesn't take control of you</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The fightstone is an organ that is in charge of <strong>willpower</strong>,<strong> motivation</strong>, and<strong> foresight. </strong>It is the duty of prospectors like Hallow to ensure we have the strength of suppress the monster inside of us. And it is Hallow's duty to defeat the awakened monsters that seek to destroy us.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3526190/extras/PlayerFightStone.png?t=1740758970\" />\u00a0\u00a0  <img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3526190/extras/StalkerFightsone.png?t=1740758970\" /> \u00a0\u00a0<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3526190/extras/GuardFightstone.png?t=1740758970\" /> </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>You're not alone in this</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Meet new friends who will support you. This isn't a burden you need to endure by yourself.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3526190/extras/hallow.png?t=1740758970\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3526190/extras/florence.png?t=1740758970\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3526190/extras/mayor.png?t=1740758970\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3526190/extras/lumni.png?t=1740758970\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Demo Features</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">An adventure with unique characters</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">7 Challenging monsters with different attack patterns and weaknesses</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">No random encounters; Enemies wander the world and will attack you</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">3 action buttons to minimize complexity - easy to learn, hard to master</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Original soundtrack and artwork </p></li></ul>","background":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/3526190?t=1740758970","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3526190/page_bg_raw.jpg?t=1740758970","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3526190/6aa1ad86d45321c9e3dabdac52fc687510177a7e/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1740758970","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3526190/6aa1ad86d45321c9e3dabdac52fc687510177a7e/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1740758970","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Game demo","id":10},{"description":"Full controller support","id":28}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"controller_support":"full","detailed_description":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>There's a FIGHTSTONE right next to your heart</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Monsters lie inside all of us. They're usually asleep but they awaken once you experience turmoil. If that happens, the prospectors will come hunting for that rock in your chest</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3526190